<title>USA: Broadway &amp; Seymour names Hall CFO.</title>
<headline>Broadway &amp; Seymour names Hall CFO.</headline>
<dateline>CHARLOTTE, N.C. 1997-06-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Broadway &amp; Seymour Inc said Friday that it has named Keith Hall chief financial officer, effective July 1, 1997.</p>
<p>Hall was previously chief financial officer for Loctite Corp. He succeeds David Finley, who will continue to serve on Broadway &amp; Seymour's board.</p>
